type.name: ObjectBounds
type.summary: Specifies the dimensions of an object.

property.name: X1
property.summary: Gets or sets the negative X-axis dimension.

property.name: X2
property.summary: Gets or sets the positive X-axis dimension.

property.name: Y1
property.summary: Gets or sets the negative Y-axis dimension.

property.name: Y2
property.summary: Gets or sets the positive Y-axis dimension.

property.name: Z1
property.summary: Gets or sets the negative Z-axis dimension.

property.name: Z2
property.summary: Gets or sets the positive Z-axis dimension.
